    const classes = useStyles()
    return(
  <div>
  <img className={classes.image}src={Profile} alt=""></img>
  <p>
  Young females are instrumental in maintaining productivity, creativity and passion within the ever-changing workplace. This is especially true for developing industries such as technology, which has a current growth rate of 4.2% and will reach a $5 trillion market value by the end of 2021. 
  Ella Smith is a Year 11 student at St Mary’s Anglican Girls’ School and is 16 years old. She comes from Three Springs, a small farming community in mid-Western Australia.  She was self-inspired to learn to code from an early age and throughout primary and high school, has developed and honed her skills. She is extremely passionate about technology and intends to finish school and complete a computer science degree.
</p><p>
